%S A393735 1,1,3,16,112,1009,10026,106744,1181868,13493188,157721486,1879935579
%N A393735 Number of free polyominoes in the {7,5} tessellation of the hyperbolic plane.
%F A393735 a(n) = P{p,q}(n) (the number of {p,q} polyominoes of size n) is equal to P{p,oo}(n) for n <= q; also P{p,q}(q+1) = P{p,oo}(q+1) + floor((p-1)/2) - floor((3+q(p-2))/2). In this case, p=7, q=5 and P{p,oo} = A005419.
%Y A393735 Cf. A333018, A393734, A393736, A393737, A393738, A005419.
%K A393735 nonn,more
%O A393735 1,3
